    "V f is free flow speed.",
    "Therefore, TPS is a value ranging from 0% to 100% where 0% is the worst traffic condition and 100% is the best.These loop detectors are deployed on freeways, including I-5, I-90, I-99, I-167, I-405, and SR-520, in the Greater Seattle Area, WA, as shown in Figure 1.",
